Samsung has launched a new competition which gives you the chance to win amazing prizes. The enter the competition, purchase any Samsung Galaxy device between 15 May and 30 June 2020. You will then be entered into a daily draw to win Samsung TVs, washing machines, and fridges. Click here to find out more about Samsung’s competition. The step-by-step details on how to enter are below. Purchase a participating product. Log on to Samsung Members and click on the benefit tab. Click on the promotion banner. Fill in your details and submit. Winners are contacted telephonically. Samsung’s range of Galaxy devices consist of its Note Series, S Series, and A Series smartphones – including the flagship Galaxy S20, S20+, and S20 Ultra devices. Please note that participants will receive an email to submit their valid proof to purchase to be entered into the draw pot. <img class="wp-image-405965 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-scaled.jpg" alt="Samsung Competition" width="640" height="336" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-300x158.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-768x403.jpg 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-1536x807.jpg 1536w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-2048x1076.jpg 2048w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Samsung-Competition-1200x630.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> This article was published in partnership with Samsung.